channel.title: Hallelujah - Rufus Wainwright midi?
channel.description:
Does anyone know of any good, free sites that have backing tracks for the song Hallelujah by Rufus Wainwright?
I've been searching for ages and can't seem to find a working link. I need it for a singing audition for Starstruck. If i can't find one i'm going to have to probably try and make my own, which will take a while. And the auditions next Friday.
Baa. Help apprecated. Kane.[br][size=1]Posted at: October 21, 2006, 02:15:26 AM[/size][hr]I've found one .. Yay.
